Friday Night Fever is going strong as the high school football season heads down the home stretch. 
For week 10, we'll have the Westwood Warriors in studio. 
The Warriors will take on Dobson Friday night, and Westwood will look to build momentum following last week's 46-41 win over Higley. 
Our game of the week will feature the Westview (7-1) at Queen Creek (6-2) matchup. 
We'll also have coverage of: 
Estrella Foothills at Cortez
